== Imɣi ines ==

Imɣi ayyi n uriḥan iṭṭuqet deg tama n wagrakal (Mediterranean Sea) n wadda d tin n ufella. D ajeğğig-is mellulen, m'ara ad ilal i yettuɣalen berrik-it m'ara yaweṭ neɣ yew, iwumi qqaren medden '''[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Illustration_Myrtus_communis0.jpg cilmun]'''. Taqbaylit tferreq yar uriḥan (imɣi) yakkid d cilmun (agummu). Ariḥan itekkar-ed, iman-is, deg teẓgi: Ur ad t-iteẓẓu bunadem ur ad t-ineqqc, ur ad isewway. 


== Timeskert ==

* Ariḥan ẓeṭṭen innaḍen yes iqerṭiyal d tiqerṭiyyal.    

* D ifer n imɣi ayi n uriḥan i tessun medden ɣer lqaɛ n uẓekka, ass m’ara tili tmettant.

* Ass n lɛid tameẓyant – ass ideg ttawṭen medden wid d tid i yasen-immuten, d aya i yettawin yidsen. Ass aneggaru n remṭan, truḥun madden truẓen-ed ariḥan, i ttarzen d taqebbiṭ meẓẓiyen. Ad ines. Azekkuyen, zik, aqbel ad tali tafat, ttekaren wid ara yeftun (ruḥen) ɣer temṭelṭ - deg leɛwayed i yfettun d tameqrant n wexxan. Ad awin yidsen lqahwa, ayefki d tkeɛkucin yakkid d uriḥan i d-rẓan iṭ izrin. Akken ara wṭenṭ lxalat ɣer temṭelṭ, ad kkent yak ɣef yiẓekwan n wid d tid i yasent-ed-ikkan. Yal tikkelt m’ara wṭenṭ ɣer yiwen n uẓekka, ad selment ɣef win / tin yemmuten, ad mmeslayent yides s teɣzef n taɣect, ad rnunt as-sersent taseṭṭa n uriḥan. 

* M’ara ad d-fakkent yak d wid d tid nsent, ad qlent ɣer wid d tin i tent-id-iqerben, alamma kkant-ed yak fell-asen(t), imir ad sersent iman nsent ɣef tama n uẓekka n win neɣ n tin yemmutend taneggarut, ad ksent lqahwa, ayefki d tkeɛkucin i yed-wwint yidsent, ad as-sqahwint, s tudrin (reminding) n w(t)in yemmuten. (Anect-ayi skurent medden deg Bgayet.)

